verbose_text: However, dietary l-isoleucine supplementation also enhanced the ileal IFNbeta (P < 0.05), IFNgamma (P < 0.05), IL-10 (P < 0.05), sIgA (P < 0.05), and IL-1beta (P = 0.07) levels and further promoted IFNbeta, IFNgamma, IL-10 and sIgA concentrations in the ileum of weaned piglets infected by RV (P < 0.05, Table XREF_TABLE).
